data.name: An error occurred while processing your request.
data.value: Terjadi kesalahan saat memproses permintaan Anda.

data.name: If you believe you should have access, please contact your system administrator. Or try signing out and signing in again.
data.value: Jika Anda yakin seharusnya memiliki akses, silakan hubungi administrator sistem Anda. Atau coba keluar dan masuk kembali.

data.name: Please check the URL and try again. If you believe this is a server error, please contact support.
data.value: Silakan periksa URL dan coba lagi. Jika Anda menganggap ini adalah kesalahan server, silakan hubungi dukungan.

data.name: Please check your request and try again. If you believe this is a server error, please contact support.
data.value: Silakan periksa permintaan Anda dan coba lagi. Jika Anda merasa ini adalah kesalahan server, silakan hubungi dukungan.

data.name: Please contact the administrator for help.
Please try again later or contact support if the problem persists.
data.value: Silakan coba lagi nanti atau hubungi dukungan jika masalahnya berlanjut.

data.name: Sorry, you do not have the necessary permissions to access this page.
data.value: Maaf, Anda tidak memiliki izin yang diperlukan untuk mengakses halaman ini.

data.name: The page you are looking for might have been removed, had its name changed, or is temporarily unavailable.
data.value: Halaman yang Anda cari mungkin telah dihapus, nama halamannya telah diubah, atau sedang tidak tersedia sementara.

data.name: We're sorry, something went wrong while processing your request.
data.value: Maaf, terjadi kesalahan saat memproses permintaan Anda.

data.name: Your browser sent a request that this server could not understand.
data.value: Browser Anda mengirim permintaan yang tidak dapat dipahami oleh server ini.
